	   <tr><td colspan=2>2hs is fine<br><br>1hs is okay, a Wurmslayer would be an improvement, a Sword of the Morning would be better, a Jeldorin or Sword of Blessings would be best.&nbsp;&nbsp;I'd just use the 2hs personally.<br><br>I'd suggest getting a Marr's Promise from Rathe Mountains for a shield.<br><br>Quest for a Kerran Toy from Kerra isle or buy a Medicine Totem.  Totem is on the expensive side.<br><br>If you feel like a slightly more expensive upgrade get a pair of Electrum Black Sapphire Earrings (2ac, 35hp, 25mana).<br><br>Get a Ry`Gorr Collar for your neck.<br><br>Get a Fine Plate Visor for your face.<br><br>Get a Deepwater Helm for your head.<br><br>Get a pair of Velium Fire Opal rings for both your fingers.<br><br>Get a crustacean bracer instead of the Erollisi bracer, or if you're rich get a pair of Deepwater bracers.<br><br>Get Deepwater arms.<br><br>Get Royal Velium gaunts from Icewell Keep for your hands (these are really good, I used them until 59 or so).<br><br>Get a Tattered mantle for your shoulders.<br><br>I assume you're a dwarf?  Get a Dusty Breastplate for your chest slot.<br><br>Back is fine.<br><br>Get a flowing black silk sash for your waist.<br><br>Get Crustacean Shell legs.<br><br>Boots are fine.<br><br>Assuming you use the 2hs and the first item listed, your stats will be adjusted as follows:<br><br>+255hp<br>-3mana<br>+70ac<br><br>-35str<br>+11sta<br>-1agi<br>0dex<br>-3wis<br>0int<br>-11cha<br><br>-15pr<br>+4mr<br>+5dr<br>-5fr<br>-5cr<br><br>Permanent haste of 21%<br><br>Using the 1hs you'll gain quite a bit more AC, lose slightly less str, and lose small amounts of MR.  HP will also increase a little bit.<br>&nbsp;<br><b>Praetor</b>, 60th Crusader<br>Avatars of Discord</td></tr>
