	   <tr><td colspan=2>I just made 45 and the stuff you got is almost like what i have on right now.<br>I dont work on 1hs but i have a ghoulbane and a charred guardian shield and most recently acquired a Cracked Darkwood Shield.<br><br>2hs: Arbitors/Soulfire<br>Range:&nbsp;&nbsp;Larktwitters Bow<br>Head:  Blackened alloy Coif or DW helm<br>Face:  Sarnak hide mask<br>Earrings:  Cougar Claw Earrings<br>Neck:  Orc Fang Necklace<br>Ring:  Velium Emerald Fire Ring/6ac 65hp ring<br>Wrist:  Iceforge Shackles/Runed Mithril Bracer<br>Arms:  Crystal Chitin Vambraces<br>Shoulders:  Obulus Death Shroud<br>Back:  Spider Fur Cloak<br>Chest: Rygorr BattleMail<br>Waist: FBSS<br>Legs:  Mithril Greaves<br>Feet:  Crustacean Boots<br>Hands:  Gauntlets of the Black<br><br>Now some of these are bought in EC for a very good price.  Some got handed down from retiring pallys who are leaving the game for DAOC.  Others like the FBSS and cougar claws can be camped to save yourself some money.  At lvl 45 I have better stats than most lvl 50's even though I am in the process of buffing up my AC that will decrease some of my strenght.  I'd advise to get yourself some Dwarven Work Boots in Unrest or save up for Crustacean Boots.  Get your guild together for a trip to Wakening Lands to do the iceforge shackle quest which was fairly easy with guildmates helping out.  Upgrade your greaves to Iceweave Leggings which drop off Gorul in GD or buy mithril/crustacean ones.  Until you level up some more there is no real better one that I can tell you about.  Hope this helps<br>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
